  "body": "# Bug\r\n\r\nThe permission tag component is too rounded. Maybe there's a quick fix, but carefully double-check if the fix is not introducing another bug, since the `border-radius` is set in a few places, including the `base-tag` component used by both `tags/permission_tag.cljs` and `tags/tag.cljs`.\r\n\r\nActual on the left side, expected on the right side.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/46027/4359234c-d157-4eee-81b6-9946a5845fc3\" width=\"800\" />\r\n\r\n### Resources\r\n\r\nDesign System - Permissions tag component - https://www.figma.com/file/WQZcp6S0EnzxdTL4taoKDv/Design-System-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=911-27048&mode=design&t=o9Dby9tUosgMJqRr-0\r\n\r\n### Implementation\r\n\r\nConsider migrating the code to latest guidelines as it is outdated.",
